[
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 77,
    "ayahArV1": "وَجَعَلْنَا ذُرِّيَّتَهُۥ هُمُ ٱلْبَاقِينَ",
    "ayahArV2": "وجعلنا ذريته هم الباقين",
    "ayahEn": "and made his descendants the sole survivors.",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 78,
    "ayahArV1": "وَتَرَكْنَا عَلَيْهِ فِى ٱلْـَٔاخِرِينَ",
    "ayahArV2": "وتركنا عليه في الاخرين",
    "ayahEn": "And We blessed him ˹with honourable mention˺ among later generations:",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 79,
    "ayahArV1": "سَلَـٰمٌ عَلَىٰ نُوحٍ فِى ٱلْعَـٰلَمِينَ",
    "ayahArV2": "سلام على نوح في العالمين",
    "ayahEn": "“Peace be upon Noah among all peoples.”",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 80,
    "ayahArV1": "إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَجْزِى ٱلْمُحْسِنِينَ",
    "ayahArV2": "انا كذلك نجزي المحسنين",
    "ayahEn": "Indeed, this is how We reward the good-doers.",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 81,
    "ayahArV1": "إِنَّهُۥ مِنْ عِبَادِنَا ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ",
    "ayahArV2": "انه من عبادنا المؤمنين",
    "ayahEn": "˹For˺ he was truly one of Our faithful servants.",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 82,
    "ayahArV1": "ثُمَّ أَغْرَقْنَا ٱلْـَٔاخَرِينَ",
    "ayahArV2": "ثم اغرقنا الاخرين",
    "ayahEn": "Then We drowned the others.",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 83,
    "ayahArV1": "۞ وَإِنَّ مِن شِيعَتِهِۦ لَإِبْرَٰهِيمَ",
    "ayahArV2": "وان من شيعته لابراهيم",
    "ayahEn": "And indeed, one of those who followed his way was Abraham.",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 84,
    "ayahArV1": "إِذْ جَآءَ رَبَّهُۥ بِقَلْبٍ سَلِيمٍ",
    "ayahArV2": "اذ جاء ربه بقلب سليم",
    "ayahEn": "˹Remember˺ when he came to his Lord with a pure heart",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 85,
    "ayahArV1": "إِذْ قَالَ لِأَبِيهِ وَقَوْمِهِۦ مَاذَا تَعْبُدُونَ",
    "ayahArV2": "اذ قال لابيه وقومه ماذا تعبدون",
    "ayahEn": "and said to his father and his people, “What are you worshipping?",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 86,
    "ayahArV1": "أَئِفْكًا ءَالِهَةً دُونَ ٱللَّهِ تُرِيدُونَ",
    "ayahArV2": "ائفكا الهة دون الله تريدون",
    "ayahEn": "Is it false gods that you desire instead of Allah?",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 87,
    "ayahArV1": "فَمَا ظَنُّكُم بِرَبِّ ٱلْعَـٰلَمِينَ",
    "ayahArV2": "فما ظنكم برب العالمين",
    "ayahEn": "What then do you expect from the Lord of all worlds?”",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 88,
    "ayahArV1": "فَنَظَرَ نَظْرَةً فِى ٱلنُّجُومِ",
    "ayahArV2": "فنظر نظرة في النجوم",
    "ayahEn": "He later looked up to the stars ˹in contemplation˺",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 89,
    "ayahArV1": "فَقَالَ إِنِّى سَقِيمٌ",
    "ayahArV2": "فقال اني سقيم",
    "ayahEn": "then said, “I am really sick.”",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 90,
    "ayahArV1": "فَتَوَلَّوْا۟ عَنْهُ مُدْبِرِينَ",
    "ayahArV2": "فتولوا عنه مدبرين",
    "ayahEn": "So they turned their backs on him and went away.",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 91,
    "ayahArV1": "فَرَاغَ إِلَىٰٓ ءَالِهَتِهِمْ فَقَالَ أَلَا تَأْكُلُونَ",
    "ayahArV2": "فراغ الى الهتهم فقال الا تاكلون",
    "ayahEn": "Then he ˹stealthily˺ advanced towards their gods, and said ˹mockingly˺, “Will you not eat ˹your offerings˺?",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 92,
    "ayahArV1": "مَا لَكُمْ لَا تَنطِقُونَ",
    "ayahArV2": "ما لكم لا تنطقون",
    "ayahEn": "What is wrong with you that you cannot speak?”",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 93,
    "ayahArV1": "فَرَاغَ عَلَيْهِمْ ضَرْبًۢا بِٱلْيَمِينِ",
    "ayahArV2": "فراغ عليهم ضربا باليمين",
    "ayahEn": "Then he swiftly turned on them, striking ˹them˺ with his right hand.",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 94,
    "ayahArV1": "فَأَقْبَلُوٓا۟ إِلَيْهِ يَزِفُّونَ",
    "ayahArV2": "فاقبلوا اليه يزفون",
    "ayahEn": "Later, his people came rushing towards him ˹furiously˺.",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 95,
    "ayahArV1": "قَالَ أَتَعْبُدُونَ مَا تَنْحِتُونَ",
    "ayahArV2": "قال اتعبدون ما تنحتون",
    "ayahEn": "He argued, “How can you worship what you carve ˹with your own hands˺",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 96,
    "ayahArV1": "وَٱللَّهُ خَلَقَكُمْ وَمَا تَعْمَلُونَ",
    "ayahArV2": "والله خلقكم وما تعملون",
    "ayahEn": "when it is Allah Who created you and whatever you do?”",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 97,
    "ayahArV1": "قَالُوا۟ ٱبْنُوا۟ لَهُۥ بُنْيَـٰنًا فَأَلْقُوهُ فِى ٱلْجَحِيمِ",
    "ayahArV2": "قالوا ابنوا له بنيانا فالقوه في الجحيم",
    "ayahEn": "They said ˹to one another˺, “Build him a furnace and cast him into the blazing fire.”",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 98,
    "ayahArV1": "فَأَرَادُوا۟ بِهِۦ كَيْدًا فَجَعَلْنَـٰهُمُ ٱلْأَسْفَلِينَ",
    "ayahArV2": "فارادوا به كيدا فجعلناهم الاسفلين",
    "ayahEn": "And so they sought to harm him, but We made them inferior.",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 99,
    "ayahArV1": "وَقَالَ إِنِّى ذَاهِبٌ إِلَىٰ رَبِّى سَيَهْدِينِ",
    "ayahArV2": "وقال اني ذاهب الى ربي سيهدين",
    "ayahEn": "He later said, “I am leaving ˹in obedience˺ to my Lord. He will guide me.",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 100,
    "ayahArV1": "رَبِّ هَبْ لِى مِنَ ٱلصَّـٰلِحِينَ",
    "ayahArV2": "رب هب لي من الصالحين",
    "ayahEn": "My Lord! Bless me with righteous offspring.”",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 101,
    "ayahArV1": "فَبَشَّرْنَـٰهُ بِغُلَـٰمٍ حَلِيمٍ",
    "ayahArV2": "فبشرناه بغلام حليم",
    "ayahEn": "So We gave him good news of a forbearing son.",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  },
  {
    "surahNo": 37,
    "ayahNo": 102,
    "ayahArV1": "فَلَمَّا بَلَغَ مَعَهُ ٱلسَّعْىَ قَالَ يَـٰبُنَىَّ إِنِّىٓ أَرَىٰ فِى ٱلْمَنَامِ أَنِّىٓ أَذْبَحُكَ فَٱنظُرْ مَاذَا تَرَىٰ ۚ قَالَ يَـٰٓأَبَتِ ٱفْعَلْ مَا تُؤْمَرُ ۖ سَتَجِدُنِىٓ إِن شَآءَ ٱللَّهُ مِنَ ٱلصَّـٰبِرِينَ",
    "ayahArV2": "فلما بلغ معه السعي قال يا بني اني ارى في المنام اني اذبحك فانظر ماذا ترى قال يا ابت افعل ما تؤمر ستجدني ان شاء الله من الصابرين",
    "ayahEn": "Then when the boy reached the age to work with him, Abraham said, “O my dear son! I have seen in a dream that I ˹must˺ sacrifice you. So tell me what you think.” He replied, “O my dear father! Do as you are commanded. Allah willing, you will find me steadfast.”",
    "meta": {
      "page": 449,
      "juz": 23,
      "hizb": 45,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    }
  }
]